      <div class="use-case">
    <h3>Design Teams</h3>
    <p>Figma real-time collaboration is essential for team design workflows. This use case demonstrates how the right tool can significantly improve productivity and outcomes. Users in this category should evaluate which platform better addresses their specific pain points and workflow requirements before making a decision.</p>
